 relates to the travel space while ensuring that every buying experience is seamless, positive and memorable.\r\nOur method is quite simple, straightforward and automated. Our fully packaged tours are waiting to be booked at the click of a button. All you have to do is check for a package that best fulfills your specific interest, follows the prompt on how to make secured payments, makes your payments and receives a notification of a successful transaction and we will mail you your travel itinerary and vouchers. You can equally put a call through to us once your payment has been made. If for any reason, you do not find a package that suits your requirement, kindly go to our customized package page and fill out the form and someone will contact you within 24hrs of your request.\r\nWe strongly believe that traveling does not have to be out of reach but affordability and budget should be a watchword in preparing all our packaged tours. We strive to give you the best package deal without breaking the bank.\r\n\r\n<b> </b>[/read][/vc_column_text][/vc_column_inner][/vc_row_inner][/vc_column][/vc_row][vc_row brando_row_style=\"color\" show_container_fluid=\"1\" brando_row_bg_color=\"#d7d9e2\" class=\"mysection\" id=\"product-offering\"][vc_column width=\"1/1\"][vc_row_inner][vc_column_inner centralized_div=\"1\" enable_clear_both=\"1\" overflow_hidden=\"1\" width=\"1/1\"][brando_section_heading brando_heading_type=\"heading-style2\" heading_preview_image=\"heading-style2\" brando_text_color=\"black-text\" brando_enable_seperator=\"1\" font_weight=\"700\" brando_heading=\"PRODUCT OFFERING\"][/vc_column_inner][/vc_row_inner][vc_row_inner equal_height=\"yes\" content_placement=\"middle\" overflow_hidden=\"1\"][vc_column_inner width=\"1/4\" class=\"po\"][brando_content_block brando_block_premade_style=\"block-4\" brando_block_preview_image=\"block-4\" brando_image=\"5643\" brando_title=\"CHEAP &amp; CHIC\"][/brando_content_block][/vc_column_inner][vc_column_inner width=\"1/4\"