(5671, 1, '2018-05-24 13:54:39', '2018-05-24 13:54:39', '[vc_row column_without_row=\"1\" show_full_width=\"1\" fullscreen=\"1\" position_relative=\"1\" overflow_hidden=\"1\" id=\"home\"][vc_column width=\"1/1\"][rev_slider alias=\"home\"][/vc_column][/vc_row][vc_row brando_row_style=\"color\" show_container_fluid=\"1\" brando_row_bg_color=\"#ffffff\" class=\"mysection\" id=\"about\"][vc_column width=\"1/1\"][vc_row_inner][vc_column_inner centralized_div=\"1\" enable_clear_both=\"1\" overflow_hidden=\"1\" width=\"1/1\"][brando_section_heading brando_heading_type=\"heading-style2\" heading_preview_image=\"heading-style2\" brando_text_color=\"black-text\" brando_enable_seperator=\"1\" font_weight=\"700\" brando_heading=\"ABOUT US\"][/vc_column_inner][/vc_row_inner][vc_row_inner equal_height=\"yes\" content_placement=\"middle\" overflow_hidden=\"1\"][vc_column_inner width=\"1/2\"][brando_simple_image brando_image=\"5606\"][/vc_column_inner][vc_column_inner width=\"1/2\"][vc_column_text]Funzania travel and tours is a travel and tour management company borne out of a genuine desire to improve the overall traveling experience of the discerning individual who seeks out a fun-filled vacation devoid of the stress of the logistic of having to book individual components of a travel itinerary.\r\n\r\nWe offer pre-packaged vacation packages for all-inclusive tours, vacations, destinations honeymoon getaways, group retreats, family reunions, staycations, milestone birthday celebrations packages while\r\ncreating a memory of a lifetime.\r\n\r\nWe pride ourselves as a pioneer brand offering this niche-based type of travel experience and our brand is positioned to change the face of travel, tourism, and hospitality in the emerging Nigeria market and in years to come, a major player in the global market.\r\n\r\n[read more=\"Click here to Read More\" less=\"Read Less\"]<b> </b>\r\n\r\nOur UVP is to make sincere connections with our clients through excellent, world best practices as it relates to the travel space while ensuring that every buying experience is seamless, positive and memorable.\r\nOur method is quite simple, straightforward and automated. Our fully packaged tours are waiting to be booked at the click of a button. All you have to do is check for a package that best fulfills your specific interest, follows the prompt on how to make secured payments, makes your payments and receives a notification of a successful transaction and we will mail you your travel itinerary and vouchers. You can equally put a call through to us once your payment has been made. If for any reason, you do not find a package that suits your requirement, kindly go to our customized package page and fill out the form and someone will contact you within 24hrs of your request.\r\nWe strongly believe that traveling does not have to be out of reach but affordability and budget should be a watchword in preparing all our packaged tours. We strive to give you the best package deal without breaking the bank.\r\n\r\n<b> </b>[/read][/vc_column_text][/vc_column_inner][/vc_row_inner][/vc_column][/vc_row][vc_row brando_row_style=\"color\" show_container_fluid=\"1\" brando_row_bg_color=\"#d7d9e2\" class=\"mysection\" id=\"offers\"][vc_column width=\"1/1\"][vc_row_inner][vc_column_inner centralized_div=\"1\" enable_clear_both=\"1\" overflow_hidden=\"1\" width=\"1/1\"][brando_section_heading brando_heading_type=\"heading-style2\" heading_preview_image=\"heading-style2\" brando_text_color=\"black-text\" brando_enable_seperator=\"1\" font_weight=\"700\" brando_heading=\"OFFERS\"][/vc_column_inner][/vc_row_inner][vc_row_inner equal_height=\"yes\" content_placement=\"middle\" overflow_hidden=\"1\"][vc_column_inner width=\"1/4\" class=\"po\"][brando_content_block brando_block_premade_style=\"block-4\" brando_block_preview_image=\"block-4\" brando_image=\"5643\" brando_title=\"CHEAP &amp; CHIC\"][/brando_content_block][/vc_column_inner][vc_column_inner width=\"1/4\" class=\"po\"][brando_content_block brando_block_premade_style=\"block-4\" brando_block_preview_image=\"block-4\" brando_image=\"5637\" brando_title=\" FOODIE VENTURE\"][/brando_content_block][/vc_column_inner][vc_column_inner width=\"1/4\" class=\"po\"][brando_content_block brando_block_premade_style=\"block-4\" brando_block_preview_image=\"block-4\" brando_image=\"5638\" brando_title=\"SPAS &amp; WELLNESS\"][/brando_content_block][/vc_column_inner][vc_column_inner width=\"1/4\" class=\"po\"][brando_content_block brando_block_premade_style=\"block-4\" brando_block_preview_image=\"block-4\" brando_image=\"5644\" brando_title=\"ADVENTURES\"][/brando_content_block][/vc_column_inner][/vc_row_inner][vc_row_inner equal_height=\"yes\" content_placement=\"middle\" overflow_hidden=\"1\"][vc_column_inner width=\"1/4\" id=\"po\" class=\"po\"][brando_content_block brando_block_premade_style=\"block-4\" brando_block_preview_image=\"block-4\" brando_image=\"5639\" brando_title=\"HONEYMOON\"][/brando_content_block][/vc_column_inner][vc_column_inner width=\"1/4\" class=\"po\"][brando_content_block brando_block_premade_style=\"block-4\" brando_block_preview_image=\"block-4\" brando_image=\"5640\" brando_title=\"BEACH RESORTS\"][/brando_content_block][/vc_column_inner][vc_column_inner width=\"1/4\" class=\"po\"][brando_content_block brando_block_premade_style=\"block-4\" brando_block_preview_image=\"block-4\" brando_image=\"5642\" brando_title=\"FAMILY VACATIONS\"][/brando_content_block][/vc_column_inner][vc_column_inner width=\"1/4\"][/vc_column_inner][/vc_row_inner][/vc_column][/vc_row][vc_row brando_row_style=\"image\" brando_image_pos_x=\"center\" brando_image_pos_y=\"top\" brando_row_image_type=\"parallax\" brando_parallax_image_type=\"parallax1\" show_container_fluid=\"1\" show_overlay=\"1\" brando_overlay_opacity=\"0.8\" brando_row_border_position=\"border-top\" class=\"mysection\" brando_row_border_color=\"#d6d6d6\" brando_border_size=\"2px\" brando_row_bg_image=\"5615\" brando_row_overlay_color=\"#0a0a0a\" brando_z_index=\"0\" id=\"why-choose-us\"][vc_column width=\"1/1\"][brando_section_heading brando_heading_type=\"heading-style2\" heading_preview_image=\"heading-style2\" brando_text_color=\"white-text\" brando_enable_seperator=\"1\" font_weight=\"700\" brando_heading=\"WHY CHOOSE US\"][vc_row_inner overflow_hidden=\"1\"][vc_column_inner width=\"1/2\"][brando_content_block brando_block_premade_style=\"block-22\" brando_block_preview_image=\"block-22\" brando_image=\"5617\" brando_title=\"INTEGRITY\" brando_title_color=\"#ffffff\"]<span style=\"color: #ffffff;\">We make it point of standard of integrity to conduct due diligence on any of our product offering to eliminate and reduce incidences of negative reviews or feedback on any of our packages because we believe in the power of positive testimonials to further push the business</span>[/brando_content_block][brando_content_block brando_block_premade_style=\"block-22\" brando_block_preview_image=\"block-22\" brando_image=\"5616\" brando_title=\"SURPRISES\" brando_title_color=\"#ffffff\"]<span style=\"color: #ffffff;\">There is always something extra we put at every location a client is vacationing in so when you arrive your destination there is a surprise waiting for you at no extra charge,now thats complimentary wont you say?</span>[/brando_content_block][/vc_column_inner][vc_column_inner width=\"1/2\"][brando_content_block brando_block_premade_style=\"block-22\" brando_block_preview_image=\"block-22\" brando_image=\"5618\" brando_title=\"NO STRESS\" brando_title_color=\"#ffffff\"]<span style=\"color: #ffffff;\">We envision perfect vacations with great hotels, amazing food, incredible sightseeing and above all, creating the perfect memories just for you. Funzania Travel and Tours stress the details so you don\'t have to.</span>[/brando_content_block][brando_content_block brando_block_premade_style=\"block-22\" brando_block_preview_image=\"block-22\" brando_image=\"5619\" brando_title=\"FANTASTIC RATES\" brando_title_color=\"#ffffff\"]<span style=\"color: #ffffff;\">You will also get fantastic rates when booking through Funzania Travel and Tours</span>[/brando_content_block][/vc_column_inner][/vc_row_inner][/vc_column][/vc_row][vc_row brando_row_style=\"color\" show_container_fluid=\"1\" brando_row_bg_color=\"#ffffff\" class=\"mysection\" id=\"tour101\"][vc_column width=\"1/1\"][vc_row_inner][vc_column_inner centralized_div=\"1\" enable_clear_both=\"1\" overflow_hidden=\"1\" width=\"1/1\"][brando_section_heading brando_heading_type=\"heading-style2\" heading_preview_image=\"heading-style2\" brando_text_color=\"black-text\" brando_enable_seperator=\"1\" font_weight=\"700\" brando_heading=\"TOUR 101\"][/vc_column_inner][/vc_row_inner][vc_row_inner equal_height=\"yes\" content_placement=\"middle\" overflow_hidden=\"1\"][vc_column_inner width=\"1/2\"][brando_simple_image brando_image=\"5622\"][/vc_column_inner][vc_column_inner width=\"1/2\"][vc_column_text]A tour is a perfectly planned vacation package and its tough putting together an ideal one.There are so many details like planning,research,logistics and reservations,there is also the language barrier issue as well as currency conversion while putting together a package.\r\n\r\nFunzania Travel and tours takes care of all that while you just go and have fun.\r\n\r\nThere is no driving,getting lost etc because the tour equally caters to that.It gets better because it gives you time to daydream in an exotic or luxurious hotel with everything at your beck and call and even more memorable nights.When you book a tour with us through any of our pre-purchased and carefully selected packages,you enjoy skipping the lines when you get to the attraction sites thereby giving you more time to enjoy the attraction as against endless hours on long and winding queues.\r\n\r\nOur tours save you two very important things MONEY and TIME.So what are you waiting for?Start booking for your next vacation now!!!!!!![/vc_column_text][/vc_column_inner][/vc_row_inner][/vc_column][/vc_row][vc_row brando_row_style=\"color\" show_container_fluid=\"1\" brando_row_bg_color=\"#00a6d8\" class=\"mysection\" id=\"contact\"][vc_column width=\"1/1\"][vc_row_inner][vc_column_inner centralized_div=\"1\" enable_clear_both=\"1\" overflow_hidden=\"1\" width=\"1/1\"][brando_section_heading brando_heading_type=\"heading-style2\" heading_preview_image=\"heading-style2\" brando_text_color=\"black-text\" brando_enable_seperator=\"1\" font_weight=\"700\" brando_heading=\"CONTACT US\"][/vc_column_inner][/vc_row_inner][vc_row_inner equal_height=\"yes\" content_placement=\"middle\" overflow_hidden=\"1\"][vc_column_inner width=\"1/4\"][/vc_column_inner][vc_column_inner width=\"1/2\"][vc_column_text]\r\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\">[contact-form-7 id=\"4\" title=\"Contact_form\"]</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: #ffffff;\"><strong>08167727723</strong></span></p>\r\n[/vc_column_text][/vc_column_inner][vc_column_inner width=\"1/4\"][/vc_column_inner][/vc_row_inner][/vc_column][/vc_row]', 'Home', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '1852-revision-v1', '', '', '2018-05-24 13:54:39', '2018-05-24 13:54:39', '', 1852, 'http://funzania.bizgrowth.com.ng/2018/05/24/1852-revision-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
