_inner][vc_column_inner width=\"1/2\"][brando_content_block brando_block_premade_style=\"block-22\" brando_block_preview_image=\"block-22\" brando_image=\"5618\" brando_title=\"NO STRESS\" brando_title_color=\"#ffffff\"]<span style=\"color: #ffffff;\">We envision perfect vacations with great hotels, amazing food, incredible sightseeing and above all, creating the perfect memories just for you. Funzania Travel and Tours stress the details so you don\'t have to.</span>[/brando_content_block][brando_content_block brando_block_premade_style=\"block-22\" brando_block_preview_image=\"block-22\" brando_image=\"5619\" brando_title=\"FANTASTIC RATES\" brando_title_color=\"#ffffff\"]<span style=\"color: #ffffff;\">You will also get fantastic rates when booking through Funzania Travel and Tours</span>[/brando_content_block][/vc_column_inner][/vc_row_inner][/vc_column][/vc_row][vc_row brando_row_style=\"color\" show_container_fluid=\"1\" brando_row_bg_color=\"#ffffff\" class=\"mysection\" id=\"tour101\"][vc_column width=\"1/1\"][vc_row_inner][vc_column_inner centralized_div=\"1\" enable_clear_both=\"1\" overflow_hidden=\"1\" width=\"1/1\"][brando_section_heading brando_heading_type=\"heading-style2\" heading_preview_image=\"heading-style2\" brando_text_color=\"black-text\" brando_enable_seperator=\"1\" font_weight=\"700\" brando_heading=\"TOUR 101\"][/vc_column_inner][/vc_row_inner][vc_row_inner equal_height=\"yes\" content_placement=\"middle\" overflow_hidden=\"1\"][vc_column_inner width=\"1/2\"][brando_simple_image brando_image=\"5712\"][/vc_column_inner][vc_column_inner width=\"1/2\"][vc_column_text]A tour is a perfectly planned vacation package and its tough putting together an ideal one.There are so many details like planning,research,logistics and reservations,there is also the language barrier issue as well as currency conversion while putting together a package.\r\n\r\nFunzania Travel and tours takes care of all that while you just go and have fun.\r\n\r\nThere is no driving,getting lost etc because the tour equally caters to that.It gets better because it gives you time to daydream in an exotic or luxurious hotel with everything at your beck and call and even more memorable nights.When you book a tour with us through any of our pre-purchased and carefully selected packages,you enjoy skipping the lines when you get to the attraction sites thereby giving you more time to enjoy the attraction as against endless hours on long and winding queues.\r\n\r\nOur tours save you two very important things MONEY and TIME.So what are you waiting for?Start booking for your next vacation now!!!!!!![/vc_column_text][/vc_column_inner][/vc_row_inner][/vc_column][/vc_row]', 'Home', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '1852-revision-v1', '', '', '2018-06-01 15:32:48', '2018-06-01 15:32:48', '', 1852, 'http://funzania.bizgrowth.com.ng/2018/06/01/1852-revision-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
