(5885, 1, '2018-06-06 13:06:22', '2018-06-06 13:06:22', '[vc_row][vc_column width=\"1/1\"][vc_column_text]This property is 3 minutes walk from the beach. Located in the North West of Mauritius, Le Palmiste features an exotic garden, only 150 m away from the beach. It offers an outdoor pool, spa facilities, and free Wi-Fi.\r\n\r\nLe Palmiste Resort &amp; Spa has air-conditioned rooms with wooden furniture. All rooms have tiled floors and balconies overlooking the garden or the pool. They also offer a satellite TV and a seating area. Guests staying in the superior room have free access to the hammam and sauna. This facility is available to guests at an additional charge.\r\n\r\nThe hotel’s restaurant serves international dishes, Mauritian specialities and lobster menus. The bar offers a selection of exotic cocktails and a variety of home-made rums.\r\n\r\nGuests can relax on the sun loungers by the pool, before enjoying various massages and Mauritian body treatments. There are also daily activities like volleyball, table tennis, and aqua gym.\r\n\r\nSir Seewoosagur Ramgoolam International Airport is 67 km away, and the hotel offers free private parking on site.\r\n\r\n<strong>TRAVEL PERIOD:    01st May – 30th June, 2018</strong>\r\n(Note: Travel date can be adjusted to suit your preferred Travel Date)[/vc_column_text][brando_popup popup_type=\"popup-form-1\" contact_forms_shortcode=\"5818\" popup_form_id=\"1528280684\" popup_button_config=\"url:http%3A%2F%2Ffunzania.bizgrowth.com.ng%2Fmauritius%2F|title:Book%20Now||\"][/brando_popup][/vc_column][/vc_row]', 'Mauritius', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '5859-revision-v1', '', '', '2018-06-06 13:06:22', '2018-06-06 13:06:22', '', 5859, 'http://funzania.bizgrowth.com.ng/2018/06/06/5859-revision-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
