(5987, 1, '2018-06-07 13:18:46', '2018-06-07 13:18:46', '[vc_row equal_height=\"yes\" content_placement=\"top\" column_without_row=\"1\" show_full_width=\"1\" overflow_hidden=\"1\"][vc_column width=\"1/2\"][brando_simple_image brando_image=\"5663\"][/vc_column][vc_column width=\"1/2\"][brando_content_block brando_block_premade_style=\"block-9\" brando_block_preview_image=\"block-9\"]<em><strong><span style=\"color: #fb39ee;\">Funzania Travel and Tours</span></strong></em> is a travel and tour management company borne out of a genuine desire to improve the overall traveling experience of the discerning individual who seeks out a fun-filled vacation devoid of the stress of the logistic of having to book individual components of a travel itinerary.\r\n\r\nWe offer pre-packaged vacation packages for all-inclusive tours, vacations, destinations honeymoon getaways, group retreats, family reunions, staycations, milestone birthday celebrations packages while creating a memory of a lifetime.\r\n\r\nWe pride ourselves as a pioneer brand offering this niche-based type of travel experience and our brand is positioned to change the face of travel, tourism, and hospitality in the emerging Nigeria market and in years to come, a major player in the global market.[/brando_content_block][/vc_column][/vc_row][vc_row][vc_column width=\"1/2\"][brando_content_block brando_block_premade_style=\"block-9\" brando_block_preview_image=\"block-9\"]Our UVP is to make sincere connections with our clients through excellent, world best practices as it relates to the travel space while ensuring that every buying experience is seamless, positive and memorable.\r\n\r\nOur method is quite simple, straightforward and automated. Our fully packaged tours are waiting to be booked at the click of a button. All you have to do is check for a package that best fulfills your specific interest, follows the prompt on how to make secured payments, makes your payments and receives a notification of a successful transaction and we will mail you your travel itinerary and vouchers. You can equally put a call through to us once your payment has been made. If for any reason, you do not find a package that suits your requirement, kindly go to our customized package page and fill out the form and someone will contact you within 24hrs of your request.\r\n\r\nWe strongly believe that traveling does not have to be out of reach but affordability and budget should be a watchword in preparing all our packaged tours. We strive to give you the best package deal without breaking the bank.[/brando_content_block][/vc_column][vc_column width=\"1/2\"][brando_simple_image brando_image=\"5644\" class=\"imgclass\"][/vc_column][/vc_row]', 'About Us', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '5687-revision-v1', '', '', '2018-06-07 13:18:46', '2018-06-07 13:18:46', '', 5687, 'http://funzania.bizgrowth.com.ng/2018/06/07/5687-revision-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0);
