den=\"1\"][vc_column_inner width=\"1/2\"][brando_simple_image brando_image=\"5712\"][/vc_column_inner][vc_column_inner width=\"1/2\"][vc_column_text]A tour is a perfectly planned vacation package and its tough putting together an ideal one. There are so many details like planning, research, logistics and reservations. There is also the language barrier issue as well as currency conversion while putting together a package.\r\n\r\n<span style=\"color: #fb39ee;\"><em><strong>Funzania Travel and Tours</strong></em></span> takes care of all that while you just go and have fun. There is no driving, getting lost etc because the tour equally caters to that.\r\n\r\nIt gets <strong>better</strong> because it gives you time to daydream in an exotic or luxurious hotel with everything at your beck and call and even more memorable nights. When you book a tour with us through any of our pre-purchased and carefully selected packages, you enjoy skipping the lines when you get to the attraction sites thereby giving you more time to enjoy the attraction as against endless hours on long and winding queues.\r\n\r\nOur tours save you two very important things <strong>MONEY</strong> and <strong>TIME</strong>. So what are you waiting for? Start booking for your next vacation now!!!!!!![/vc_column_text][/vc_column_inner][/vc_row_inner][/vc_column][/vc_row][vc_row brando_row_style=\"image\" brando_image_pos_x=\"center\" brando_image_pos_y=\"top\" brando_row_image_type=\"parallax\" brando_parallax_image_type=\"parallax1\" show_container_fluid=\"1\" show_overlay=\"1\" brando_overlay_opacity=\"0.8\" brando_row_border_position=\"border-top\" class=\"mysection\" brando_row_border_color=\"#d6d6d6\" brando_border_size=\"2px\" brando_row_bg_image=\"5644\" brando_row_overlay_color=\"#0a0a0a\" brando_z_index=\"0\" id=\"why-choose-us\"][vc_column width=\"1/1\"][brando_section_heading brando_heading_type=\"heading-style2\" heading_preview_image=\"heading-style2\" brando_text_color=\"white-text\" brando_enable_seperator=\"1\" font_weight=\"700\" brando_heading=\"WHY CHOOSE US\"][vc_row_inner equal_height=\"yes\" content_placement=\"middle\" overflow_hidden=\"1\"][vc_column_inner width=\"1/2\"][brando_content_block brando_block_premade_style=\"block-22\" brando_block_preview_image=\"block-22\" brando_image=\"5618\" brando_title=\"NO STRESS\" brando_title_color=\"#ffffff\"]<span style=\"color: #ffffff;\">We envision perfect vacations with great hotels, amazing food, incredible sightseeing and above all, creating the perfect memories just for you. Funzania Travel and Tours stress the details so you don\'t have to.</span>[/brando_content_block][/vc_column_inner][vc_column_inner width=\"1/2\"][brando_content_block brando_block_premade_style=\"block-22\" brando_block_preview_image=\"block-22\" brando_image=\"5617\" brando_title=\"INTEGRITY\" brando_title_color=\"#ffffff\"]<span style=\"color: #ffffff;\">We make it point of standard of integrity to conduct due diligence on any of our product offering to eliminate and reduce incidences of negative reviews or feedback on any of our packages because we believe in the power of positive testimonials to further push the business</span>[/brando_content_block][/vc_column_inner][/vc_row_inner][vc_row_inner equal_height=\"yes\" content_placement=\"middle\"][vc_column_inner width=\"1/2\"][brando_content_block brando_block_premade_style=\"block-22\" brando_block_preview_image=\"block-22\" brando_image=\"5616\" brando_title=\"SURPRISES\" brando_title_color=\"#ffffff\"]<span style=\"color: #ffffff;\">There is always something extra we put at every location a client is vacationing in so when you arrive your destination there is a surprise waiting for you at no extra charge,now thats complimentary wont you say?</span>[/brando_content_block][/vc_column_inner][vc_column_inner width=\"1/2\"][brando_content_block brando_block_premade_style=\"block-22\" brando_block_preview_image=\"block-22\" brando_image=\"5619\" brando_title=\"FANTASTIC RATES\" brando_title_color=\"#ffffff\"]<span style=\"color: #ffffff;\">You will also get fantastic rates when booking through Funzania Travel and Tours</span>[/brando_content_block][/vc_column_inner][/vc_row_inner][/vc_column][/vc_row]', 'Inspire Me', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '5673-revision-v1', '', '', '2018-06-07 13:28:55', '2018-06-07 13:28:55', '', 5673, 'http://funzania.bizgrowth.com.ng/2018/06/07/5673-revision-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
