;\">Our UVP is to make sincere connections with our clients through excellent...</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: left; line-height: 30px;\"><a class=\"inner-link highlight-button-dark btn-round btn-medium button btn alt-font\" href=\"/about-us/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">Read More</a></p>\r\n[/vc_column_text][/vc_column_inner][/vc_row_inner][/vc_column][/vc_row][vc_row brando_row_style=\"color\" show_container_fluid=\"1\" class=\"mysection\"][vc_column width=\"1/1\"][vc_row_inner overflow_hidden=\"1\"][vc_column_inner width=\"1/1\"][brando_section_heading brando_heading_type=\"heading-style2\" heading_preview_image=\"heading-style2\" brando_text_color=\"black-text\" brando_enable_seperator=\"1\" font_weight=\"700\" brando_heading=\"OFFERS\"][/vc_column_inner][/vc_row_inner][vc_row_inner equal_height=\"yes\" content_placement=\"middle\" overflow_hidden=\"1\"][vc_column_inner width=\"1/3\" class=\"po\"][vc_column_text]\r\n<p style=\"min-height: 260px; max-height: 260px;\"><a href=\"/tours\"><img class=\"aligncenter wp-image-5790 size-full\" src=\"https://funzaniatravelandtours.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/06/WhatsApp-Image-2018-05-29-at-12.45.11-PM.jpeg\" alt=\"\" width=\"100%\" height=\"100%\" /></a></p>\r\n[/vc_column_text][/vc_column_inner][vc_column_inner width=\"1/3\" class=\"po\"][vc_column_text]\r\n<p style=\"min-height: 260px; max-height: 260px;\"><a href=\"/tours\"><img class=\"aligncenter wp-image-5791 size-full\" src=\"https://funzaniatravelandtours.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/06/WhatsApp-Image-2018-05-29-at-1.08.25-PM.jpeg\" alt=\"\" /></a></p>\r\n[/vc_column_text][/vc_column_inner][vc_column_inner width=\"1/3\"][vc_column_text]\r\n<p style=\"min-height: 260px; max-height: 260px;\"><a href=\"/tours\"><img class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-5789\" src=\"https://funzaniatravelandtours.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/06/WhatsApp-Image-2018-05-29-at-1.08.24-PM.jpeg\" alt=\"\" width=\"100%\" height=\"100%\" /></a></p>\r\n[/vc_column_text][/vc_column_inner][/vc_row_inner][/vc_column][/vc_row][vc_row brando_row_style=\"color\" show_container_fluid=\"1\" brando_row_bg_color=\"#ffffff\" class=\"mysection\" id=\"tour101\"][vc_column width=\"1/1\"][vc_row_inner][vc_column_inner centralized_div=\"1\" enable_clear_both=\"1\" overflow_hidden=\"1\" width=\"1/1\"][brando_section_heading brando_heading_type=\"heading-style2\" heading_preview_image=\"heading-style2\" brando_text_color=\"black-text\" brando_enable_seperator=\"1\" font_weight=\"700\" brando_heading=\"TOUR 101\"][/vc_column_inner][/vc_row_inner][vc_row_inner equal_height=\"yes\" content_placement=\"middle\" overflow_hidden=\"1\"][vc_column_inner width=\"1/2\"][brando_simple_image brando_image=\"5712\"][/vc_column_inner][vc_column_inner width=\"1/2\"][vc_column_text]A tour is a perfectly planned vacation package and its tough putting together an ideal one. There are so many details like planning, research, logistics and reservations. There is also the language barrier issue as well as currency conversion while putting together a package.\r\n\r\n<span style=\"color: #fb39ee;\"><em><strong>Funzania Travel and Tours</strong></em></span> takes care of all that while you just go and have fun. There is no driving, getting lost etc because the tour equally caters to that.\r\n\r\nIt gets <strong>better</strong> because it gives you time to daydream in an exotic or luxurious hotel with everything at your beck and call and even more memorable nights. When you book a tour with us through any of our pre-purchased and carefully selected packages, you enjoy skipping the lines when you get to the attraction sites thereby giving you more time to enjoy the attraction as against endless hours on long and winding queues.\r\n\r\nOur tours save you two very important things <strong>MONEY</strong> and <strong>TIME</strong>. So what are you waiting for? Start booking for your next vacation now!!!!!!![/vc_column_text][/vc_column_inner][/vc_row_inner][/vc_column][/vc_row][vc_row brando_row