_block_premade_style=\"block-22\" brando_block_preview_image=\"block-22\" brando_image=\"5616\" brando_title=\"SURPRISES\" brando_title_color=\"#ffffff\"]<span style=\"color: #ffffff;\">There is always something extra we put at every location a client is vacationing in so when you arrive your destination there is a surprise waiting for you at no extra charge,now thats complimentary wont you say?</span>[/brando_content_block][/vc_column_inner][vc_column_inner width=\"1/2\"][brando_content_block brando_block_premade_style=\"block-22\" brando_block_preview_image=\"block-22\" brando_image=\"5619\" brando_title=\"FANTASTIC RATES\" brando_title_color=\"#ffffff\"]<span style=\"color: #ffffff;\">You will also get fantastic rates when booking through Funzania Travel and Tours</span>[/brando_content_block][/vc_column_inner][/vc_row_inner][/vc_column][/vc_row]', 'Home', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '1852-revision-v1', '', '', '2018-06-07 17:44:10', '2018-06-07 17:44:10', '', 1852, 'https://funzaniatravelandtours.com/2018/06/07/1852-revision-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
